Package: SpliceImpactR
Type: Package
Title: An R pacakge to identify functional impacts due to alternative splicing events 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Zachary Wakefield
Maintainer: Zachary Wakefield <zachpw@bu.edut>
Description: SpliceImpactR employs 4 primary methods—differential inclusion analysis, 
  primary sequence analysis, domain analysis, and isoform-specific domain-derived protein-protein 
  interactions (ISPPI) —to elucidate the proteomic consequences of AS events.
